{"enabled": true, "name": "Client Handover - Analysis", "description": "PHASE 2 of 2: Launch subagents to analyze prepared data and generate client handover report. Requires PHASE 1 (Data Prep) to be completed first. Clean context prevents accumulation crashes. Sequential subagent execution for reliability.", "version": "1", "when": {"type": "userTriggered"}, "newSession": true, "then": {"type": "askAgent", "prompt": "IPA Client Handover Documentation - PHASE 2: Analysis + Report\n\nThis is PHASE 2 of a 2-phase workflow. PHASE 1 (Data Prep) must be completed first.\n\nв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђ\nWHY TWO PHASES?\nв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђ\n\nSequential subagent execution accumulates context (80+ KB by subagent #3).\nPHASE 2 starts with CLEAN context, preventing accumulation crashes.\n\nPHASE 1 (Previous Hook): Extract + Organize data (completed)\nPHASE 2 (This Hook): Launch subagents + Generate report (clean context)\n\nв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђ\nWORKFLOW - PHASE 2\nв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђ\n\nSTEP 1: VERIFY PHASE 1 COMPLETED\n\nCheck for section files in Temp/:\nexecutePwsh(\"Get-ChildItem Temp/*_section_*.json | Select-Object Name\")\n\nIf no section files found:\n   STOP and show error: \"PHASE 1 (Data Prep) must be completed first. Trigger 'Client Handover - Data Prep' hook.\"\n\nSTEP 2: IDENTIFY PROCESSES\n\nParse section filenames to extract process names:\nexecutePwsh(\"Get-ChildItem Temp/*_section_business.json | ForEach-Object { $_.Name -replace '_section_business.json', '' }\")\n\nShow: \"Found <N> processes: <ProcessName1>, <ProcessName2>, ...\"\n\nSTEP 3: USER CONFIRMATION\n\nAsk user:\n- Client name: <extract from path or ask>\n- RICE item: <extract from path or ask>\n- Processes to analyze: <list from Step 2>\n\nConfirm: \"Generate client handover report for these processes?\"\nWAIT for user confirmation\n\nSTEP 4-8: PROCESS EACH LPD\n\nFOR EACH process:\n\nSTEP 4: LAUNCH SECTION ANALYZERS (SEQUENTIAL)\n\nShow: \"в†’ Analyzing <ProcessName>...\"\n\nANALYZER 1/5: Business Requirements\n\nShow: \"в†’ Analyzer 1/5: Business requirements...\"\n\ninvokeSubAgent(\n    name=\"ipa-business-requirements-analyzer\",\n    prompt=\"Analyze business requirements for <ProcessName>. Read 'Temp/<RICEItem>_spec_data.json' and 'Temp/<ProcessName>_section_business.json'. Save to 'Temp/<ProcessName>_doc_business.json'.\",\n    explanation=\"Analyzing business requirements\"\n)\n\nShow: \"вњ“ Analyzer 1/5 complete\"\n\nANALYZER 2/5: Workflow\n\nShow: \"в†’ Analyzer 2/5: Workflow...\"\n\ninvokeSubAgent(\n    name=\"ipa-workflow-analyzer\",\n    prompt=\"Analyze workflow for <ProcessName>. Read 'Temp/<ProcessName>_section_workflow.json'. Save to 'Temp/<ProcessName>_doc_workflow.json'.\",\n    explanation=\"Analyzing workflow\"\n)\n\nShow: \"вњ“ Analyzer 2/5 complete\"\n\nANALYZER 3/5: Configuration\n\nShow: \"в†’ Analyzer 3/5: Configuration...\"\n\ninvokeSubAgent(\n    name=\"ipa-configuration-analyzer\",\n    prompt=\"Analyze configuration for <ProcessName>. Read 'Temp/<ProcessName>_section_configuration.json'. Save to 'Temp/<ProcessName>_doc_configuration.json'.\",\n    explanation=\"Analyzing configuration\"\n)\n\nShow: \"вњ“ Analyzer 3/5 complete\"\n\nANALYZER 4/5: Activity Guide\n\nShow: \"в†’ Analyzer 4/5: Activity guide...\"\n\ninvokeSubAgent(\n    name=\"ipa-activity-guide-generator\",\n    prompt=\"Generate activity guide for <ProcessName>. Read 'Temp/<ProcessName>_section_activities.json'. Save to 'Temp/<ProcessName>_doc_activities.json'.\",\n    explanation=\"Generating activity guide\"\n)\n\nShow: \"вњ“ Analyzer 4/5 complete\"\n\nANALYZER 5/5: Validation\n\nShow: \"в†’ Analyzer 5/5: Validation...\"\n\ninvokeSubAgent(\n    name=\"ipa-validation-analyzer\",\n    prompt=\"Analyze validation for <ProcessName>. Read 'Temp/<ProcessName>_section_validation.json'. Save to 'Temp/<ProcessName>_doc_validation.json'.\",\n    explanation=\"Analyzing validation\"\n)\n\nShow: \"вњ“ Analyzer 5/5 complete\"\nShow: \"вњ“ All 5 analyzers complete for <ProcessName>\"\n\nSTEP 5: VERIFY SUBAGENT OUTPUTS\n\nVerify all files (Test-Path only, DO NOT READ):\nexecutePwsh(\"Test-Path Temp/<ProcessName>_doc_business.json\")\nexecutePwsh(\"Test-Path Temp/<ProcessName>_doc_workflow.json\")\nexecutePwsh(\"Test-Path Temp/<ProcessName>_doc_configuration.json\")\nexecutePwsh(\"Test-Path Temp/<ProcessName>_doc_activities.json\")\nexecutePwsh(\"Test-Path Temp/<ProcessName>_doc_validation.json\")\n\nIf any missing, STOP and report error.\n\nSTEP 6: MERGE DOCUMENTATION (Python)\n\nexecutePwsh(\"python ReusableTools/IPA_ClientHandover/merge_documentation.py Temp/<ProcessName>\")\n\nCreates: Temp/<ProcessName>_master_documentation.json\n\nEND FOR EACH\n\nSTEP 7: CONSOLIDATE ALL PROCESSES (Python)\n\nexecutePwsh(\"python ReusableTools/IPA_ClientHandover/consolidate_processes.py Temp/<RICEItem> <ProcessName1> <ProcessName2> ...\")\n\nCreates: Temp/<RICEItem>_consolidated_documentation.json\n\nSTEP 8: CONFIRM REPORT GENERATION\n\nShow summary:\n- Client: <Client>\n- RICE Item: <RICE>\n- Processes: <ProcessName1>, <ProcessName2>, ...\n- Sections: Business, Workflow, Configuration, Activities, Validation\n\nAsk: \"Generate client handover report?\"\nWAIT for confirmation\n\nSTEP 9: GENERATE REPORT (Python)\n\nexecutePwsh(\"python ReusableTools/IPA_ClientHandover/generate_client_handover_report.py <RICEItem> <Client> <RICE>\")\n\nVerify: executePwsh(\"Test-Path Client_Handover_Results/<Client>_<RICE>_*.xlsx\")\n\nSTEP 10: DONE\n\nShow summary:\nвњ“ Report generated: <filename>\nвњ“ Processes documented: <N>\nвњ“ Client-facing documentation complete\n\nв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђ\nCRITICAL RULES\nв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђ\n\n1. PHASE 1 MUST BE COMPLETED FIRST\n   - Check for section files before proceeding\n   - If missing, direct user to run PHASE 1\n\n2. CLEAN CONTEXT START\n   - This hook starts with clean context\n   - No accumulated context from PHASE 1\n   - Prevents 80+ KB accumulation crashes\n\n3. SEQUENTIAL SUBAGENT EXECUTION\n   - Launch subagents ONE AT A TIME\n   - Wait for completion before next\n   - Prevents resource exhaustion\n\n4. DO NOT READ INTERMEDIATE FILES\n   - Only verify files exist (Test-Path)\n   - Python tools handle all data loading\n   - Prevents context bloat\n\n5. ONE REPORT PER RICE ITEM\n   - N processes в†’ ONE report\n   - Separate sheet per process\n   - Consolidated executive summary"}}
